      <div class="py-2">
        <text class="text-lg">
          I'm product manager working at <a href="https://www.betrybe.com/" style="text-decoration: underline">Trybe</a>, an online school of technology. Aside from product, I spend time on robotics projects and programming challenges. Check out my work below.
          </text
        >
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/rodonoah" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
        <!-- <a href="https://github.com/manuelernestog/astro-modern-personal-website" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5"> Get This template</a> -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
